This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) and Natural Language Processing (cs.CL) sub-categories, as it deals with generating textual descriptions of images. The use of a Convolutional Neural Network (CNN) for image representation and a language model for generating descriptions also suggests that it could fall under the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper mentions using statistics and metrics to evaluate the model's performance, which could also place it under the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category.
